<expan>Parsperg<ex>er</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>Parsperg</expan><lb/><expan>Görg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Frawnberg<ex>er</ex></expan> zum Hag dem
                            <expan>jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan><lb/>Gebharten Judman zu Affeckln
                                <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>.<lb/><expan>Ausgenom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        dem <expan>Parsperg<ex>er</ex></expan> geendert: ettlich zeit
                                her.<lb/><expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan>
<expan>Wilhelm<ex>en</ex></expan> vom Wolffstein hat man
                                <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> niht
                            <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, wan er knecht und pferd in der
                        laistung hett. </ab>
